object: Sreelekha Mitra (Bengali: শ্রীলেখা মিত্র) (born 30 August 1971) is a Bengali Indian actress of TV and films. She has won an Anandalok Award (2006) and BFJA Award (2007) for acting. She is also a judge in a Bengali standup comedy show, Mirakkel. Mitra appeared in a Coca-Cola ad  with Aamir Khan.
